text: The area of Shiraoi District in Iburi Subprefecture. is a district located in Iburi Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 20,866 and a density of 49.01 persons per km². The total area is 425.75 km². ==Towns and villages== *Shiraoi Category:Districts in Hokkaido
title: Shiraoi District, Hokkaido
